2011-11-25

Original Realtek RTL2832U chipset (DVB) Linux 2.6.x driver
Rel. 2.2.2

Thanks to Realtek

This driver is a full version using DVB-T/C DTMB and 10 tuners
modded for Linux kernel 3.0.0

!! WORK IN PROGRESS , ALPHA STATE !!


** FRESH INSTALL **

- install linux headers
sudo apt-get install linux-headers-$(uname -r)

- install git
sudo apt-get install git

- clone this repo using git
git clone git@github.com:ambrosa/DVB-Realtek-RTL2832U-2.2.2-10tuner-mod_kernel-3.0.0.git 

- goto into source dir
cd DVB-Realtek-RTL2832U-2.2.2-10tuner-mod_kernel-3.0.0
cd RTL2832-2.2.2_kernel-3.0.0

- compile code
make clean
make

- install module
sudo make install

- insert module (or reboot)
modprobe dvb_usb_rtl2832u

- Module dvb_usb_rtl2832u has many options (use modinfo dvb_usb_rtl2832u to see them)

- if you want enable basic debug (default disabled) use
modprobe dvb_usb_rtl2832u debug=1
- if you want enable remote_command (default disabled) use
modprobe dvb_usb_rtl2832u rc_mode=2  (or =0 or =1)


** UPDATING ALREADY EXISTING LOCAL GIT REPO WITH NEW CHANGES **

- goto into main repo dir
cd DVB-Realtek-RTL2832U-2.2.2-10tuner-mod_kernel-3.0.0

- update local files with new changes
git pull

- compile 
cd RTL2832-2.2.2_kernel-3.0.0
make clean
make

- install module
sudo make install

